About Me

I'm Zainab — a frontend developer with a creative soul and a technical brain. From a young age, I’ve been obsessed with crafting things — whether through code, art, or design. Balancing my O-Levels with development projects, I’ve learned to thrive in both structured learning and self-driven discovery.

My focus lies in building beautiful, accessible websites that are responsive, animated, and enjoyable to use. I’m always learning — currently diving deeper into Next.js, animation libraries, and UI/UX design systems.

My Core Skills

React.js
Next.js
HTML / CSS / JavaScript
TypeScript
Git & GitHub
Responsive Design
UI/UX Thinking
Team Collaboration

My Journey So Far

✦ Started web development with curiosity and YouTube tutorials.
✦ Completed Bano Qabil’s tech program and started working on real projects.
✦ Built multiple websites including portfolios, e-commerce, and landing pages.
✦ Interned in a software house and began taking freelance inquiries.
✦ Now blending creativity with code to build meaningful products while finishing school.
